Disney has just opened their first-ever overwater villas & bungalows at the Polynesian Villas & Bungalows in Orlando . 
  The resort is located on the shores of the Seven Seas Lagoon . 
  Each bungalow has two bedrooms, two bathrooms and a private plunge pool . 
  The villas are available from $2,000 a night - rising to $4,500 at peak times . 
 